# Local API base URL (optional)
#
# Dev (recommended):
# - Leave `VITE_API_BASE_URL` empty and use the Vite dev proxy in `vite.config.ts`
#   so requests like `/api/auth/login` are forwarded to `http://localhost:8080`.
#
# Direct backend calls:
# - Set `VITE_API_BASE_URL` (example below). If you do this, your Spring Boot app
#   must allow CORS for the frontend origin (e.g. `http://localhost:3000`).
#
# Usage:
# - Create `.env.local` (gitignored) and put your local values there.
#
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8080

